{"tid":547030,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"劉江華：高球場年辦12萬場活動","createTime":"2018-02-01T04:59:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-03T11:07:05.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"242730ea668ec846c9e1f749b42ba15f229d827e","tid":547030,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T04:59:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180201/20291797\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180201%2F20291797&d=tKULNKj27C%2FG92dllZ2ZRNU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=1a063ed1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180201%2F20291797&h=3d04d405\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180201/20291797</a><br />\n<br />\n劉江華：高球場年辦12萬場活動<br />\n<br />\n要聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<br />\n民政局長劉江華<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】粉嶺高爾夫球場契約兩年後屆滿，近年有意見要求收回興建公營房屋。政府2014年成立跨部門工作小組檢討私人遊樂場地契約政策，惟至今3年未有結果。民主派批評政府不負責任、走數。民政局長劉江華則力撐高球場有貢獻，稱每年舉行約12萬場高球活動，公眾使用量逾四成。<br />\n<br />\n立法會昨討論檢討私人遊樂場地契約政策。民主黨立法會議員尹兆堅批評，港府拖延提交報告，令土地供應專責小組三度延期，無法討論相關議程。公民黨陳淑莊也指，1977年康體局只花兩年時間完成同類報告，政府原承諾2014年提交初步報告，批評劉江華走數。<br />\n<br />\n自由黨邵家輝撐保留高球場，指球場每年舉辦的部份國際賽事，吸引全球好手來港參賽，若撥出地皮建屋，擔心本港失去國際高球場的地位。劉江華表示，由於涉及檢討60多個契約及不同形式的體育會，也需跨部門審議，故需時較長，今年會向立會交代檢討結果。<br />\n<br />\n他指粉嶺高球場去年舉行約12萬場高球運動，當中非會員佔約5萬場，佔總使用量逾四成；每年舉辦的賽事多達28項，其中香港高爾夫球公開賽已舉行59屆。不過，尹兆堅質疑數據，因12萬場高球活動相當於每日舉行329場，公眾竟佔192場。劉指數據來自高球場，稱是事實陳述。<br />\n<br />\n■記者王家文"},{"pid":"3bddf37a3e9c4f91a3e0e19b46190612bcc09875","tid":547030,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T05:00:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n笑死， 咁都講得出。"},{"pid":"9ffa848db1d94427a1a9506207c1ee44cf01b049","tid":547030,"uid":5686,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"quote":{"pid":"3bddf37a3e9c4f91a3e0e19b46190612bcc09875","tid":547030,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T05:00:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n笑死， 咁都講得出。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T05:01:54.000Z","msg":"開24 都要一分鐘4.376場<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5ca8a9ce699d777be07e5b9fe70d6137863c6eb","tid":547030,"uid":44916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T05:02:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好笑"},{"pid":"04ccd56330cc909b9f06932a92af9021043c7c93","tid":547030,"uid":33878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T05:02:23.000Z","msg":"打golf 重要過住屋問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4a714029ff5fb089858dfd1062643e9db1a28e8","tid":547030,"uid":5686,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"04ccd56330cc909b9f06932a92af9021043c7c93","tid":547030,"uid":33878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T05:02:23.000Z","msg":"打golf 重要過住屋問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T05:05:14.000Z","msg":"你問連登仔都會話香港無住屋問題,<br />\n無/未有錢買樓=&gt;同老豆老母住.<br />\n有錢=&gt;去供樓.<br />\n<br />\n咁個住屋問題係邊?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n樓市Gogogo"},{"pid":"d9a255bd9582600c1b51253fa5c78135e0fc50d9","tid":547030,"uid":550,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T05:07:20.000Z","msg":"灣仔場使用率夠去到100%啦<br />\n之前689話要拆又唔見你走出嚟反